    <summary>
      <para>
        <b>Type: <b><see cref="EXIT_THREAD_DEBUG_INFO" /></b></b>
      </para>
      <para>If the <b>dwDebugEventCode</b> is <b>EXIT_THREAD_DEBUG_EVENT</b></para>
      <para>(4), <b>u.ExitThread</b> specifies an
<see cref="EXIT_THREAD_DEBUG_INFO" /> structure.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
